程序包 org.cloudbus.cloudsim

类 CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.CloudletScheduler
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.CloudletSchedulerTimeShared
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload
public class CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload
extends CloudletSchedulerTimeShared
CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload implements a policy of scheduling performed by a virtual machine to run its Cloudlets, assuming there is just one cloudlet which is working as an online service. It extends a TimeShared policy, but in fact, considering that there is just one cloudlet for the VM using this scheduler, the cloudlet will not compete for CPU with other ones. Each VM has to have its own instance of a CloudletScheduler.
从以下版本开始:
CloudSim Toolkit 2.0

    • CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload

      public CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload​(double mips, int numberOfPes)
      Instantiates a new VM scheduler
      参数:
      mips - The individual MIPS capacity of each PE allocated to the VM using the scheduler, considering that all PEs have the same capacity.
      numberOfPes - The number of PEs allocated to the VM using the scheduler.
